#!/usr/local/projects/routing/help/html_filter.pl
<h2 align=center>Help for "Account password"</h2>
To use this software, you must login to the Brightsands software suite.
If you are seeing this prompt, it means that you can create an account for
yourself, if you are creating an account, you're going to have to type
the password twice.
<p>
You don't need to fill this in if the account already exists and you
are just logging in.
